01:00:03,140 --> 01:00:05,945
You're not the only one who thinks so!

830
01:00:06,059 --> 01:00:07,582
Are you trying to cover Misa?

831
01:00:08,594 --> 01:00:13,224
I don't know much about her yet since we've just started dating

832
01:00:13,598 --> 01:00:15,594
I can't believe that she's Kira

833
01:00:16,426 --> 01:00:18,346
Of course, I'm not conscious of Kira in me

834
01:00:18,347 --> 01:00:19,683
but,

835
01:00:20,481 --> 01:00:22,535
I might have a multiple personality

836
01:00:23,679 --> 01:00:24,905
I want you to figure it out

837
01:00:24,906 --> 01:00:27,334
We investigated you, but couldn't find anything suspicious

838
01:00:27,917 --> 01:00:30,235
But we watched over him only when he was home

839
01:00:30,756 --> 01:00:33,444
We don't know exactly what he did outside

840
01:00:34,042 --> 01:00:37,715
Then tie his arms and legs and keep him under surveillance

841
01:00:37,750 --> 01:00:38,627
This time

842
01:00:40,364 --> 01:00:42,641
It's an around-the-clock surveillance

843
01:00:44,011 --> 01:00:45,625
That'll be fine with me

844
01:00:46,657 --> 01:00:48,213
But if,

845
01:00:48,704 --> 01:00:51,743
new crimes are committed while I'm under surveillance...

846
01:00:52,181 --> 01:00:54,081
and Kira punishes the criminals

847
01:00:54,927 --> 01:00:56,043
When it happens

848
01:00:56,706 --> 01:00:58,845
We'll certainly free you

849
01:01:01,804 --> 01:01:02,647
Thank you

850
01:01:11,124 --> 01:01:11,730
Light...

851
01:01:13,325 --> 01:01:14,441
Do you really mean it?

852
01:01:35,090 --> 01:01:37,321
Where's Light?

853
01:01:39,094 --> 01:01:41,499
What happened to our son?

854
01:01:42,097 --> 01:01:44,079
Dad, why don't you say something?

855
01:01:44,099 --> 01:01:45,379
Dear

856
01:02:36,085 --> 01:02:38,818
"Celebrating LIght's 18th birthday"

857
01:02:40,657 --> 01:02:44,322
"This is a rulebook which was based on human wisdom"

858
01:02:44,357 --> 01:02:46,990
"which still struggles to answer what justice is"

859
01:02:47,395 --> 01:02:48,459
"Thanks, dad!"

860
01:02:49,098 --> 01:02:51,081
"I want to study and think about what justice is"

861
01:02:56,105 --> 01:03:01,129
Amane Misa: Surveillance Day 8

862
01:03:02,601 --> 01:03:03,604
Yagami Light: Surveillance Day 3

863
01:03:05,934 --> 01:03:07,389
How is it, Ryuzaki?

864
01:03:09,084 --> 01:03:11,632
Has kira killed anyone yet?

865
01:03:13,719 --> 01:03:16,759
There's no activities so far

866
01:03:18,409 --> 01:03:20,485
No criminals have been killed

867
01:03:21,667 --> 01:03:22,744
Is that so...

868
01:03:25,100 --> 01:03:28,488
Then I'm getting even more suspicious.

869
01:03:29,567 --> 01:03:31,682
I'm soooo bored!

870
01:03:32,107 --> 01:03:33,670
I can't eat apples

871
01:03:34,109 --> 01:03:36,275
and I can't even talk with you.

872
01:03:37,112 --> 01:03:39,841
I wonder how Rem's doing now

873
01:04:16,084 --> 01:04:19,856
Where's my ID card?

874
01:04:20,637 --> 01:04:22,121
Does anyone know?

875
01:05:01,526 --> 01:05:03,139
Don't make a sound

876
01:05:03,857 --> 01:05:06,537
I brought a little gift for you

877
01:05:10,105 --> 01:05:12,107
Misa. Day 12
Light: Day 7

878
01:05:12,142 --> 01:05:14,075
I want to see Light

879
01:05:15,110 --> 01:05:17,112
I want to see Light, stalkers!

880
01:05:17,147 --> 01:05:19,046
Dad, mom

881
01:05:21,083 --> 01:05:22,136
Light,

882
01:05:22,559 --> 01:05:24,352
You look exhausted

883
01:05:26,580 --> 01:05:27,840
Are you okay?

884
01:05:30,092 --> 01:05:32,667
Yeah, I know I look so miserable right now

885
01:05:34,096 --> 01:05:36,820
But I don't care about such as useless pride..

886
01:05:39,056 --> 01:05:39,775
"I discard it"

887
01:05:41,103 --> 01:05:43,170
You "discard" it?

888
01:05:43,792 --> 01:05:45,896
You'll lose your memory

889
01:05:46,108 --> 01:05:48,076
Alright, Light.

890
01:05:49,111 --> 01:05:51,045
Goodbye

891
01:06:13,927 --> 01:06:14,749
Ryuzaki...

892
01:06:16,561 --> 01:06:17,406
What's wrong?

893
01:06:19,107 --> 01:06:22,094
I know I asked you to do this to me

894
01:06:23,111 --> 01:06:25,053
But now I surely know..

895
01:06:26,992 --> 01:06:28,396
This is a waste of time

896
01:06:29,746 --> 01:06:31,317
I'm not Kira

897
01:06:32,076 --> 01:06:35,207
I'll be the judge of that, not you

898
01:06:36,270 --> 01:06:38,272
It's totally impossible to do such cruel things

899
01:06:38,307 --> 01:06:40,067
without being conscious

900
01:06:41,678 --> 01:06:42,605
Don't you think so?

901
01:06:43,745 --> 01:06:46,388
It was you who said that you might be Kira

902
01:06:47,123 --> 01:06:48,942
without being conscious

903
01:06:49,283 --> 01:06:51,276
While I'm here, I clearly saw my goal

904
01:06:51,986 --> 01:06:54,776
I won't let Kira go free, he drove me into a corner

905
01:06:55,289 --> 01:06:56,497
Ryuzaki!

906
01:06:56,498 --> 01:06:59,342
Let's cooperate and find a way to reach Kira!

907
01:06:59,970 --> 01:07:03,717
We can get him!

908
01:07:04,890 --> 01:07:08,061
Light...
suddenly became so positive

909
01:07:25,286 --> 01:07:27,843
Misa: Day 19
Light: Day 14

910
01:07:28,064 --> 01:07:30,760
Since he offered to do it, but

911
01:07:31,444 --> 01:07:33,096
I'm worried about Misa

912
01:07:37,450 --> 01:07:38,891
She's a tough kid

913
01:07:39,452 --> 01:07:41,323
If I were her, I'd go insane

914
01:07:49,297 --> 01:07:49,900
Ryuzaki!

915
01:07:51,636 --> 01:07:52,584
Kira is back!

916
01:07:53,638 --> 01:07:55,930
Criminals are dying of heart attack one after another

917
01:07:58,643 --> 01:07:59,202
Light!

918
01:08:00,198 --> 01:08:02,946
There's been no action from Kira for 2 weeks.

919
01:08:04,200 --> 01:08:05,430
It's time you admit that you're Kira

920
01:08:05,465 --> 01:08:06,148
Hey!

921
01:08:08,267 --> 01:08:11,559
If you see only the current situation, I'm guilty. But this is a trap...

922
01:08:13,098 --> 01:08:15,649
I said I'm not Kira!
Believe me!

923
01:08:39,877 --> 01:08:42,424
Why did Kira... choose me as his replacement?

924
01:08:43,621 --> 01:08:47,499
You often predicted who'll be the next target of Kira

925
01:08:48,589 --> 01:08:51,729
You must have noticed the reason through your reports

926
01:08:59,937 --> 01:09:01,939
Kira's punishment...

927
01:09:01,974 --> 01:09:04,942
...is nearly the same as my view on justice

928
01:09:05,448 --> 01:09:06,527
That's what I thought

929
01:09:13,765 --> 01:09:16,373
Kira is just trying to make the world a better place

930
01:09:16,920 --> 01:09:20,320
It's my mission to tell the people that he's doing the right thing

931
01:09:21,230 --> 01:09:23,831
If I were Kira, I would use the media more efficiently!

932
01:09:24,928 --> 01:09:29,952
That makes you the most suitable person as Kira's partner

933
01:09:30,780 --> 01:09:31,890
That is the reason

934
01:09:32,936 --> 01:09:34,965
Kira chose me as his partner...

935
01:09:46,917 --> 01:09:50,876
Misa: Day 23
Light: Day 18

936
01:09:52,936 --> 01:09:56,486
Criminals are constantly being killed

937
01:09:57,928 --> 01:09:59,930
Even the ones they never knew

938
01:09:59,965 --> 01:10:03,752
It's impossible to kill them in this situation

939
01:10:06,937 --> 01:10:08,353
For example,

940
01:10:09,060 --> 01:10:10,936
if the Kira's ability has been transferred to another person

941
01:10:11,758 --> 01:10:13,701
and the person has become the Third Kira

942
01:10:14,266 --> 01:10:16,724
and they've lost their memories

943
01:10:16,947 --> 01:10:18,582
It explains everything

944
01:10:19,426 --> 01:10:20,257
Even if you were right,

945
01:10:20,899 --> 01:10:22,532
there's no way to prove it

946
01:10:28,636 --> 01:10:29,404
Ryuzaki

947
01:10:32,678 --> 01:10:35,243
Why don't we try a different approach?

948
01:10:52,147 --> 01:10:53,912
How do you feel?

949
01:10:57,152 --> 01:10:58,902
Good, thanks

950
01:10:59,154 --> 01:11:01,061
I'm impressed with your courage

951
01:11:03,158 --> 01:11:06,479
Still, we have the evidence found in Amane's room

952
01:11:07,086 --> 01:11:11,399
You can't go outside until we solve the case

953
01:11:12,167 --> 01:11:13,972
If I have to stay here anyway

954
01:11:15,033 --> 01:11:17,923
Let me go back to the team and help you find Kira

955
01:11:18,173 --> 01:11:21,660
Yes, I was thinking about the exact same thing

956
01:11:22,713 --> 01:11:27,808
You have to stay with me all day and assist me

957
01:11:29,151 --> 01:11:30,551
Thanks, Ryuzaki

958
01:11:31,853 --> 01:11:33,379
Let's find Kira together

959
01:11:42,136 --> 01:11:43,231
I love you...

960
01:11:44,166 --> 01:11:45,690
Light

961
01:12:00,194 --> 01:12:01,896
Ms Wakita!
Are you okay?

962
01:12:01,884 --> 01:12:03,137
What happened to you?

963
01:12:03,822 --> 01:12:04,734
Get an ambulance!

964
01:12:11,159 --> 01:12:12,215
She's dead

965
01:12:13,532 --> 01:12:16,935
Her name is Wakita Masako and she was wanted for

966
01:12:17,165 --> 01:12:19,765
killing her colleague when she was working in a nightclub

967
01:12:20,936 --> 01:12:21,973
Is this another case

968
01:12:21,974 --> 01:12:24,437
of punishment from Kira?

969
01:12:25,173 --> 01:12:31,322
We found Wakita's address and tried to interview her

970
01:12:31,522 --> 01:12:33,314
but she died in front of us

971
01:12:34,066 --> 01:12:36,471
Ms. Takada, you must be shocked

972
01:12:37,152 --> 01:12:39,154
She did not have any health problem

973
01:12:39,189 --> 01:12:43,113
so it is natural to think that she was killed by Kira

974
01:12:44,550 --> 01:12:46,477
Now please look at this graph

975
01:12:47,452 --> 01:12:50,634
This is the result of a poll taken from 1000 people in Japan

976
01:12:51,166 --> 01:12:53,168
According to the result,

977
01:12:53,203 --> 01:12:55,649
60% of them are supporting Kira

978
01:12:55,684 --> 01:12:57,137
This is surprising isn't it?

979
01:12:57,172 --> 01:12:58,508
I don't think so

980
01:12:59,174 --> 01:13:01,176
Considering that the crime rate has been decreasing

981
01:13:03,983 --> 01:13:06,137
by the appearance of Kira, this result is expected

982
01:13:09,151 --> 01:13:11,119
Not bad

983
01:13:12,702 --> 01:13:15,529
This is a fact that Kira is fighting against evil

984
01:13:16,929 --> 01:13:19,106
What is the true justice?

985
01:13:20,052 --> 01:13:22,225
Does the police, or L, really can help us?

986
01:13:23,031 --> 01:13:24,684
Kira is trying to make us thing.

987
01:13:25,167 --> 01:13:26,758
She's good

988
01:13:29,171 --> 01:13:31,191
We can't blame her because

989
01:13:32,439 --> 01:13:35,635
We haven't found any clues to go on

990
01:13:37,179 --> 01:13:39,123
What's wrong Ryuzaki?
It's not like you

991
01:13:40,673 --> 01:13:42,641
Oh, great work!

992
01:13:44,204 --> 01:13:45,217
Thank you for supervising

993
01:13:45,505 --> 01:13:46,992
Your comments were witty

994
01:13:48,944 --> 01:13:49,942
Thank you so much!

995
01:13:51,109 --> 01:13:52,519
The director said that...

996
01:13:53,161 --> 01:13:55,065
you'd be a good anchor

997
01:13:55,741 --> 01:13:56,385
Really?

998
01:13:57,187 --> 01:14:00,321
for being critical towards the society through Kira's case...

999
01:14:00,744 --> 01:14:03,877
Your brave, intelligent attitude has attracted the viewers.

1000
01:14:05,798 --> 01:14:07,940
You're becoming more attractive

1001
01:14:09,042 --> 01:14:10,029
Mr. Demegawa!

1002
01:14:13,125 --> 01:14:15,121
Could you ask your boss?

1003
01:14:16,131 --> 01:14:18,147
to spray pesticide in the studio

1004
01:14:18,719 --> 01:14:21,115
since a noisy bug's flying around here

1005
01:14:21,736 --> 01:14:22,885
Saeko!

1006
01:14:23,158 --> 01:14:24,490
Let's go have dinner?

1007
01:14:27,007 --> 01:14:27,836
Kiyomi

1008
01:14:28,754 --> 01:14:30,840
You know, each employee has an appropriate role, right?

1009
01:14:31,127 --> 01:14:32,466
What is your role, then?

1010
01:14:33,630 --> 01:14:35,923
No one's listening to your trashy comments!

1011
01:14:36,818 --> 01:14:37,543
Let's go

1012
01:14:44,179 --> 01:14:48,209
I say she's too fugly to be the anchor for our show!

1013
01:14:48,718 --> 01:14:49,810
Oh, come on

1014
01:14:50,152 --> 01:14:52,972
We employees can't say no to your boss, you know.

1015
01:14:53,689 --> 01:14:54,934
Are you kidding me?

1016
01:14:55,157 --> 01:14:57,920
You're the one who said no to your boss and showed Kira's video!

1017
01:14:59,005 --> 01:15:00,420
You slept with her, didn't you?

1018
01:15:01,677 --> 01:15:04,997
There's nobody but you who got a job by sleeping with me

1019
01:15:06,982 --> 01:15:07,962
Stop the car

1020
01:15:07,963 --> 01:15:08,931
Huh?

1021
01:15:09,171 --> 01:15:10,598
Stop the car now!

1022
01:15:19,564 --> 01:15:20,923
I'll never forgive her!

1023
01:15:22,173 --> 01:15:22,913
Hey, wait!

1024
01:15:23,902 --> 01:15:24,821
Calm down!

1025
01:15:26,335 --> 01:15:27,557
What's the matter with you!

1026
01:15:31,518 --> 01:15:33,693
You can't catch a taxi here!

1027
01:15:49,716 --> 01:15:50,810
Good evening

1028
01:15:54,149 --> 01:15:55,012
Good evening

1029
01:15:55,459 --> 01:15:58,832
Welcome to Evening Spot,
I'm Takada Kiyomi, the new anchor

1030
01:16:00,627 --> 01:16:01,569
First of all,

1031
01:16:02,157 --> 01:16:04,853
I have to announce a sad news

1032
01:16:06,665 --> 01:16:10,669
Last night, Nishiyama Saeko, our excellent former anchor,

1033
01:16:10,165 --> 01:16:12,730
died of a car accident

1034
01:16:14,169 --> 01:16:16,137
She was, for me..

1035
01:16:17,172 --> 01:16:18,784
a few years senior than me

1036
01:16:19,174 --> 01:16:22,595
and one of the person I respected the most

1037
01:16:24,587 --> 01:16:27,556
It is very sad that...

1038
01:16:28,149 --> 01:16:30,517
my first job as an anchor is

1039
01:16:32,009 --> 01:16:33,720
to announce about Saeko's death

1040
01:16:38,511 --> 01:16:41,157
This feels like being on a honeymoon!

1041
01:16:43,164 --> 01:16:46,167
If I can always spend my time with you like this

1042
01:16:46,202 --> 01:16:48,283
I won't want to go back to work

1043
01:16:51,172 --> 01:16:56,230
But, if they lock me up again, I'll die!

1044
01:16:57,829 --> 01:16:58,635
Oh, sorry!

1045
01:17:03,151 --> 01:17:04,504
Light

1046
01:17:05,153 --> 01:17:05,793
Are you studying?

1047
01:17:05,828 --> 01:17:08,206
Sorry Misa, can you please leave me alone for a while?

1048
01:17:26,579 --> 01:17:27,590
I'll go downstairs

1049
01:17:28,523 --> 01:17:29,498
Dont leave me alone

1050
01:17:35,672 --> 01:17:37,632
Light, come back soon, okay?

1051
01:17:38,153 --> 01:17:40,955
I'm sorry, but I'll set you free soon

1052
01:17:55,547 --> 01:17:57,415
Ryuzaki is a little depressed

1053
01:17:58,103 --> 01:18:00,583
Yeah, because he lost all his clues...

1054
01:18:02,639 --> 01:18:04,067
You're too loud

1055
01:18:04,179 --> 01:18:05,430
Ryuzaki!

1056
01:18:06,147 --> 01:18:07,160
Please be honest

1057
01:18:07,618 --> 01:18:09,752
What is the percentage that I'm Kira?

1058
01:18:11,152 --> 01:18:14,272
The percentage that you are Kira is...

1059
01:18:15,043 --> 01:18:16,033
nearly zero

1060
01:18:16,941 --> 01:18:17,419
I see

1061
01:18:19,160 --> 01:18:19,901
Great

1062
01:18:20,545 --> 01:18:21,296
I'm so happy

1063
01:18:22,163 --> 01:18:26,167
I'm also happy that you don't seem to be Kira, but

1064
01:18:27,333 --> 01:18:29,676
at the same time I lost all the clues

1065
01:18:31,127 --> 01:18:32,754
There's a vital clue

1066
01:18:33,721 --> 01:18:34,604
What if I said so?

1067
01:18:36,275 --> 01:18:37,834
When will you come back?

1068
01:18:38,179 --> 01:18:39,365
Are you serious?

1069
01:18:40,148 --> 01:18:41,000
Look at this

1070
01:18:45,153 --> 01:18:47,819
The red one is Kira's action before I was confined

1071
01:18:48,538 --> 01:18:49,841
and the blue one is his new action.

1072
01:18:49,157 --> 01:18:53,008
I profiled them statistically

1073
01:18:53,161 --> 01:18:56,159
Are these the same person?

1074
01:18:56,164 --> 01:18:57,148
No

1075
01:18:57,484 --> 01:18:59,159
They have some differences

1076
01:19:05,545 --> 01:19:06,742
Oh, they really do!

1077
01:19:08,176 --> 01:19:11,179
Even if you try to imitate someone's movement

1078
01:19:11,214 --> 01:19:13,097
you can't hide your habits or personality

1079
01:19:14,113 --> 01:19:16,650
They appear to be a remarkable tendency

1080
01:19:17,152 --> 01:19:18,329
Ryuzaki...

1081
01:19:19,029 --> 01:19:20,187
He's got the energy again!

1082
01:19:20,382 --> 01:19:21,317
I bet you know it

1083
01:19:22,433 --> 01:19:25,370
If Kira before and after the restraint were the same person

1084
01:19:25,405 --> 01:19:27,644
THe distribution wouldn't be so different

1085
01:19:28,789 --> 01:19:31,097
It means that they are different person and

1086
01:19:31,166 --> 01:19:33,772
we can see the distinct characterists that show their tendencies

1087
01:19:35,170 --> 01:19:36,115
How is it , Ryuzaki?

1088
01:19:37,130 --> 01:19:37,888
Doesn't it give you some motivation?

1089
01:19:39,009 --> 01:19:40,970
Yes Light, that you so much

1090
01:19:42,430 --> 01:19:43,673
By the way, what are the characteristics?

1091
01:19:44,893 --> 01:19:47,628
Well, the first characteristic is publicity

1092
01:19:47,862 --> 01:19:52,491
I mean, the new Kira cares slightly more about cases featured by the media

1093
01:19:53,425 --> 01:19:55,098
And the second factor is

1094
01:19:55,133 --> 01:19:56,676
gender

1095
01:19:56,871 --> 01:20:01,513
The new one focuses on more cases related to women

1096
01:20:02,414 --> 01:20:03,992
This Kira may be a woman

1097
01:20:04,695 --> 01:20:06,164
And the third factor is...

1098
01:20:07,582 --> 01:20:10,055
which might be the answer already

1099
01:20:10,585 --> 01:20:11,915
What? Oh come one Light, tell us

