1136
01:23:27,997 --> 01:23:29,024
You're right...

1137
01:23:29,238 --> 01:23:29,941
One more thing

1138
01:23:30,889 --> 01:23:34,079
What she's writing down on the right page now..

1139
01:23:34,436 --> 01:23:36,128
