1160
01:25:27,092 --> 01:25:28,245
I'm the one who called you

1161
01:25:35,392 --> 01:25:36,382
"Miatsuo Yosuke"

1162
01:25:36,417 --> 01:25:40,691
If I die, the tapes will automatically go public

1163
01:25:41,431 --> 01:25:44,434
