1166
01:25:52,117 --> 01:25:55,093
Transfer 5 million yen to my account

1167
01:25:56,087 --> 01:25:58,089
Once payment is confirmed

1168
01:25:58,124 --> 01:25:59,802
I'll give you the tapes

1169
01:26:01,092 --> 01:26:02,558
