01:26:08,430 --> 01:26:11,168
It's me. Kiyomi. turn on the TV

1171
01:26:11,398 --> 01:26:12,410
Sakura TV

1172
01:26:13,104 --> 01:26:14,061
Why?

1173
01:26:14,603 --> 01:26:16,217
No reason, just turn on the TV

1174
01:26:22,204 --> 01:26:24,560
Kira is a woman?

1175
01:26:25,116 --> 01:26:27,587
Wow, I couldn't think of it

1176
01:26:27,825 --> 01:26:28,544
"Special Program: Chasing Kira's Identity"

1177
01:26:28,977 --> 01:26:31,277
I have the tapes as evidence

1178
01:26:31,485 --> 01:26:33,959
