01:28:14,001 --> 01:28:15,088
Rem, what's going on?

1205
01:28:16,611 --> 01:28:17,122
"Rem.."

1206
01:28:18,727 --> 01:28:20,028
What is "Rem"?

1207
01:28:20,444 --> 01:28:21,130
Who is she talking to?

1208
01:28:25,355 --> 01:28:26,606
A Death God?

1209
01:28:29,086 --> 01:28:32,641
"Matsuo Yosuke"
It must be a false name!

1210
01:28:33,542 --> 01:28:36,123
Rem! You must've known it since you're the Death God!

1211
01:28:36,158 --> 01:28:38,082
You didn't tell me!

1212
01:28:38,824 --> 01:28:42,297
She often says "Death God"

1213
01:28:42,332 --> 01:28:43,822
Is it a code or something?

1214
01:28:45,089 --> 01:28:47,057
The most logical way is to think that

1215
01:28:48,485 --> 01:28:49,858
the Death God exists

1216
01:28:51,010 --> 01:28:51,669
What?

1217
01:28:52,682 --> 01:28:52,962
Okay

1218
01:28:54,564 --> 01:28:55,353
Let's make a deal

1219
01:28:56,709 --> 01:28:57,709
Give me the Death God's eyes!

1220
01:29:02,692 --> 01:29:04,810
The Death God's eyes...?

1221
01:29:08,450 --> 01:29:10,017
