1222
01:29:11,701 --> 01:29:13,682
The Second Kira has the ability to kill only by the faces

1223
01:29:15,470 --> 01:29:16,923
That's "the Death God's eye"

1224
01:30:31,361 --> 01:30:31,825
Roll down the window

1225
01:30:37,692 --> 01:30:38,585
Show me your ID

1226
01:30:40,882 --> 01:30:41,711
You don't have it?

1227
01:30:43,323 --> 01:30:46,026
Don't look at me like that, the rule is the rule

1228
01:30:47,678 --> 01:30:49,724
Shidohara Genta

1229
01:30:51,695 --> 01:30:52,651
How did you know my name?

1230
01:30:56,831 --> 01:30:57,599
Wait!

1231
01:30:58,635 --> 01:31:00,614
Do you appear on TV?

1232
01:31:02,322 --> 01:31:03,825
Something TV...

1233
01:31:04,837 --> 01:31:05,992
You're an anchor, right?

1234
01:31:07,365 --> 01:31:08,266
What are you doing?

1235
01:31:08,945 --> 01:31:09,868
Wait!

1236
01:31:44,029 --> 01:31:47,116
A policeman fell down, but I can't help him!

1237
01:31:47,843 --> 01:31:48,504
Got it

1238
01:31:49,845 --> 01:31:50,650
Did she use "the eye"?

1239
01:31:51,697 --> 01:31:53,524
It's too dangerous to let her go any further

1240
01:31:54,496 --> 01:31:58,887
We don't know how she did it, but it's better to catch her

1241
01:32:51,359 --> 01:32:52,500
Freeze!

1242
01:32:58,728 --> 01:33:00,030
Let me go!

1243
01:33:13,994 --> 01:33:14,711
Let me go!

1244
01:33:22,759 --> 01:33:26,248
We have watched every single action you made

1245
01:33:28,490 --> 01:33:30,655
The TV program was a fake

1246
01:33:32,326 --> 01:33:33,132
It was a trap!

1247
01:33:33,494 --> 01:33:34,399
Takada Kiyomi!

1248
01:33:36,428 --> 01:33:37,969
How did you do that?

1249
01:33:39,500 --> 01:33:40,663
Are you a detective?

1250
01:33:40,970 --> 01:33:41,447
As Kira..

1251
01:33:42,660 --> 01:33:44,033
How did you kill those people?

1252
01:33:46,474 --> 01:33:48,252
You wrote the names on the notebook

1253
01:33:53,481 --> 01:33:56,030
After writing them down.. what did you do?

1254
01:33:58,286 --> 01:33:59,115
I just write them down

1255
01:33:59,487 --> 01:34:01,020
I said what did you do after!

1256
01:34:03,490 --> 01:34:04,774
Then why don't you try it?

1257
01:34:10,498 --> 01:34:12,500
You write names down and...

1258
01:34:13,003 --> 01:34:14,353
the person whose name is written dies

1259
01:34:15,176 --> 01:34:16,149
The notebook of the Death God

1260
01:34:29,904 --> 01:34:31,828
What the...

1261
01:34:33,488 --> 01:34:34,895
Dad, what's wrong?

1262
01:34:44,499 --> 01:34:47,310
When you touch it, you can see the Death God?

1263
01:34:55,263 --> 01:34:57,124
Ryuzaki, let me touch it!

1264
01:35:13,681 --> 01:35:15,772
