1265
01:35:17,498 --> 01:35:19,466
yeah

1266
01:35:24,381 --> 01:35:25,143
I won!

1267
01:35:26,062 --> 01:35:27,539
Everything's under control

1268
01:35:31,479 --> 01:35:35,753
If only I touch the Death Note, my memory will come back

1269
01:35:36,484 --> 01:35:37,443
Is this really true?

1270
01:35:38,213 --> 01:35:38,858
Yes, but

1271
01:35:39,393 --> 01:35:43,147
you can remember it only when you touch the Death Note

1272
01:35:43,182 --> 01:35:46,517
