1275
01:35:54,469 --> 01:35:58,721
While you have the memory, kill the former owner

1276
01:35:59,371 --> 01:36:02,337
Good.
That explanation is enough

1277
01:36:03,064 --> 01:36:03,781
Rem

1278
01:36:04,313 --> 01:36:06,281
Give this to the Third Kira

1279
01:36:07,172 --> 01:36:09,515
If you're the Death God, you can find a suitable one

1280
01:36:10,233 --> 01:36:14,159
And after 13 days, let that person resume Kira's job

1281
01:36:14,813 --> 01:36:16,250
I can choose anyone?

1282
01:36:17,276 --> 01:36:21,928
As you won't remember, you can't reach the new owner

1283
01:36:22,741 --> 01:36:25,569
