1286
01:36:32,142 --> 01:36:35,793
I'll touch the Note before L, or at the same time

1287
01:36:37,478 --> 01:36:38,472
And one more thing

1288
01:36:39,480 --> 01:36:41,977
I have something I want you to write down on the Note

1289
01:36:42,483 --> 01:36:43,701
