1292
01:37:03,241 --> 01:37:04,814
The Death God exists

1293
01:37:04,849 --> 01:37:06,219
That explains everything

1294
01:37:06,416 --> 01:37:09,108
Now I know how they kill

1295
01:37:10,062 --> 01:37:11,669
If you write down a person's name on the notebook

1296
01:37:12,481 --> 01:37:14,109
that person dies!

1297
01:37:15,271 --> 01:37:16,811
