1301
01:37:30,498 --> 01:37:31,560
That's right

1302
01:37:31,794 --> 01:37:33,513
I didn't kill anybody

1303
01:37:34,407 --> 01:37:36,042
I just wrote down the names

1304
01:37:36,950 --> 01:37:37,401
No

1305
01:37:38,533 --> 01:37:40,876
If we can prove that the notebook kills people

1306
01:37:41,961 --> 01:37:43,102
You'll be guilty

1307
01:37:43,920 --> 01:37:44,597
Death Penalty

1308
01:37:52,486 --> 01:37:54,488
Humans, listen!

1309
01:37:56,032 --> 01:37:58,453
I'm the Death God, Rem

1310
01:37:59,223 --> 01:38:02,132
Only the humans who touched the Death Note can see me

1311
01:38:02,573 --> 01:38:05,267
I can see your lifespan

1312
01:38:06,128 --> 01:38:08,971
And I can take your lives away

1313
01:38:10,471 --> 01:38:14,430
So you'd better not make me angry

1314
01:38:16,084 --> 01:38:19,470
The Death Note has the power of the Death God

1315
01:38:20,481 --> 01:38:22,476
That woman is correct

1316
01:38:22,483 --> 01:38:26,533
the humans whose name is written on the Death Note shall die

1317
01:38:27,163 --> 01:38:28,496
"Takada Kiyomi"

1318
01:38:28,701 --> 01:38:33,008
With so called Death Note you can control the dying situations, can't you?

1319
01:38:35,703 --> 01:38:37,733
Why don't you try it yourself

1320
01:38:38,501 --> 01:38:40,669
by writing her name on the Note?

1321
01:38:41,503 --> 01:38:43,113
Rem, what do you...

1322
01:39:03,100 --> 01:39:03,513
Takada!

1323
01:39:12,026 --> 01:39:12,911
She's dead...

1324
01:39:17,321 --> 01:39:19,324
Light, hand me the notebook

1325
01:39:37,491 --> 01:39:38,818
Overall

1326
01:39:39,360 --> 01:39:41,710
Why did Takada Kiyomi die?

1327
01:39:42,496 --> 01:39:44,915
Accidental heart attack or...

1328
01:39:45,382 --> 01:39:46,099
suicide...?

1329
01:39:47,753 --> 01:39:48,863
Killed by other Kira?

1330
01:39:50,471 --> 01:39:52,439
What do you think, Death God?

1331
01:39:53,087 --> 01:39:54,346
Don't ask me

1332
01:39:57,678 --> 01:40:01,207
The name on the notebook and the dead criminals are the same, but

1333
01:40:01,413 --> 01:40:03,376
there's no name before Light's confinement

1334
01:40:05,486 --> 01:40:06,657
What do you think?

1335
01:40:07,166 --> 01:40:11,390
The owner of the Note might die when the ownership moves to the other

1336
01:40:12,332 --> 01:40:14,343
The First and the Second Kira might have already...

1337
01:40:15,496 --> 01:40:17,142
I see. Now Takada has died

1338
01:40:17,992 --> 01:40:21,208
and the ownership of this notebook has transferred to someone else

1339
01:40:21,559 --> 01:40:22,826
What do you think, Death God?

1340
01:40:23,625 --> 01:40:24,573
Don't ask me

1341
01:40:25,723 --> 01:40:28,097
Who owns the Note now?

1342
01:40:28,957 --> 01:40:29,957
I cannot answer

1343
01:40:31,183 --> 01:40:33,562
Is that the only thing you can say?

1344
01:40:34,214 --> 01:40:35,065
By the way

1345
01:40:37,410 --> 01:40:40,292
about the last rule of this Death Note

1346
01:40:41,536 --> 01:40:46,887
"If the owner does not write any name for 13 days"

1347
01:40:47,587 --> 01:40:48,427
"the owner shall die"

1348
01:40:49,997 --> 01:40:53,956
Considering this rule, the former Kiras have died

1349
01:40:54,513 --> 01:40:56,978
Then Light, who was under surveillance for 18 days?

1350
01:40:57,167 --> 01:41:01,265
and Amane, which was 23 days, are completely innocent

1351
01:41:01,797 --> 01:41:02,876
Death God!

1352
01:41:04,965 --> 01:41:08,430
Are all the rules on this notebook true?

1353
01:41:10,946 --> 01:41:12,643
Yes, they are

1354
01:41:16,079 --> 01:41:19,222
I got it, Light and Misa are free now

1355
01:41:21,026 --> 01:41:23,529
Light, call your mother and go home

1356
01:41:23,564 --> 01:41:24,047
Dad!

1357
01:41:24,501 --> 01:41:27,629
I'd like to stay here and continue working..

1358
01:41:28,536 --> 01:41:29,615
I think I have to

1359
01:41:31,340 --> 01:41:31,896
Ryuzaki

1360
01:41:33,595 --> 01:41:34,851
You need me, don't you?

1361
01:41:36,544 --> 01:41:40,749
I got it.
Light, stay here and help us

1362
01:41:41,736 --> 01:41:43,959
This looks like a common notebook

1363
01:41:44,660 --> 01:41:47,368
I can't believe this thing can kill people

1364
01:41:48,217 --> 01:41:48,903
What?

1365
01:41:49,251 --> 01:41:51,163
Why don't you come with me?

1366
01:41:51,355 --> 01:41:52,783
You can come whenever you want

1367
01:41:53,365 --> 01:41:54,391
Ryuzaki will allow us

1368
01:41:55,083 --> 01:41:56,470
to just talk at the entrance

1369
01:41:57,849 --> 01:41:59,220
Right, I'll come see you everyday

1370
01:41:59,923 --> 01:42:00,663
Be prepared!

1371
01:42:07,528 --> 01:42:08,324
Misa...

1372
01:42:08,883 --> 01:42:09,966
Listen quietly

1373
01:42:13,347 --> 01:42:14,642
Will you do me a favor?

1374
01:42:17,272 --> 01:42:18,342
What is it?

1375
01:42:31,604 --> 01:42:32,584
It's here!

1376
01:43:13,274 --> 01:43:14,961
Light is the Kira...

1377
01:43:17,229 --> 01:43:18,650
He's my God!

1378
01:43:22,027 --> 01:43:23,442
So happy

1379
01:43:24,769 --> 01:43:26,374
My Light is the Kira...!

1380
01:43:29,378 --> 01:43:32,300
I'm back at last!

1381
01:43:34,089 --> 01:43:34,927
Ryuk!

1382
01:43:36,712 --> 01:43:37,812
Why are you here?

1383
01:43:38,714 --> 01:43:40,969
That Death Note is mine

1384
01:43:42,010 --> 01:43:43,956
So this time I'll follow you

1385
01:43:45,263 --> 01:43:48,101
Don't worry, your memory won't be gone

1386
01:43:48,384 --> 01:43:51,758
If you become the owner of this Note

1387
01:43:54,272 --> 01:43:55,710
Okay, I'll be the owner

1388
01:43:57,275 --> 01:43:58,543
Oh, I almost forgot!

1389
01:44:03,281 --> 01:44:04,008
Here

1390
01:44:04,365 --> 01:44:05,365
A gift from Light!

1391
01:44:07,285 --> 01:44:08,634
App.. Apple

1392
01:44:08,978 --> 01:44:11,045
Oh Light... !
He's more generous than he looks!

1393
01:44:14,588 --> 01:44:15,169
"Dear Misa"

1394
01:44:16,261 --> 01:44:21,165
"When you read this letter, you must've remembered everything."

1395
01:44:22,267 --> 01:44:24,779
"To create an ideal world together."

1396
01:44:25,418 --> 01:44:27,949
"You must resume punishing instead of me."

1397
01:44:29,750 --> 01:44:30,442
"And one more thing."

1398
01:44:31,242 --> 01:44:35,674
"do you remember the guy named Ryuzaki I introduced you at my college?"

1399
01:44:36,787 --> 01:44:39,716
"He's our enemy, L"

1400
01:44:41,286 --> 01:44:42,201
That guy is L?

1401
01:44:43,181 --> 01:44:47,117
"You must've seen his real name with your Death God's eye."

1402
01:44:48,260 --> 01:44:50,531
"Write down the name on the Death Note"

1403
01:44:50,902 --> 01:44:52,249
"and eliminate L."

1404
01:44:56,954 --> 01:44:58,352
Elminate L...

1405
01:45:12,283 --> 01:45:12,958
Damn it!

1406
01:45:14,286 --> 01:45:16,144
I can't remember it!

1407
01:45:18,110 --> 01:45:22,046
I saw names of hundreds of people everyday

1408
01:45:23,551 --> 01:45:27,510
Once you discard the ownership, you lose the ability of "the eye"

1409
01:45:28,266 --> 01:45:30,352
I'm sorry, Misa

1410
01:45:33,771 --> 01:45:35,136
Ryuk

1411
01:45:37,491 --> 01:45:38,984
Make the eye-deal again

1412
01:45:39,557 --> 01:45:40,493
Are you sure?

1413
01:45:41,866 --> 01:45:43,979
You've already lost half of your lifespan

1414
01:45:44,653 --> 01:45:46,317
You'll lose the half of if

1415
01:45:46,784 --> 01:45:48,909
I know!

1416
01:45:50,258 --> 01:45:53,142
I don't want to lose my face!

1417
01:45:53,758 --> 01:45:54,298
Face....

1418
01:45:55,751 --> 01:45:57,153
but you have the face.

1419
01:45:57,912 --> 01:45:59,349
Don't take it literally!

1420
01:46:01,437 --> 01:46:03,943
Well, I don't understand human mind really...

1421
01:46:04,389 --> 01:46:06,304
You want the Death God's eye

1422
01:46:10,775 --> 01:46:12,855
I have to obey Light...

1423
01:46:23,637 --> 01:46:25,480
Just one week after Takada's death...

1424
01:46:27,694 --> 01:46:29,297
The new Kira has appeared!

1425
01:46:30,591 --> 01:46:31,828
Criminals are being killed again

1426
01:46:32,547 --> 01:46:35,443
It means there are more notebooks

1427
01:46:36,768 --> 01:46:37,692
Just after,

1428
01:46:39,107 --> 01:46:40,559
Amane Misa was freed

1429
01:46:41,741 --> 01:46:42,331
Ryuzaki!

1430
01:46:43,289 --> 01:46:44,159
Don't give me that again!

1431
01:46:44,404 --> 01:46:46,815
Don't you remember the 13 day rule?

1432
01:46:47,405 --> 01:46:48,043
Mr Yagami

1433
01:46:49,335 --> 01:46:50,134
What?

1434
01:46:50,169 --> 01:46:53,731
Let's inspect this notebook

1435
01:46:55,630 --> 01:46:59,330
I'll ask FBI and have them provide us with two prisoners from the death row

1436
01:46:59,791 --> 01:47:02,133
We'll make the prisoners A write the name of the B

1437
01:47:02,583 --> 01:47:03,583
to see if B will die

1438
01:47:05,654 --> 01:47:09,613
then leave A from the Note for 13 days to see if A will die

1439
01:47:10,768 --> 01:47:14,684
I can't believe you treat human lives like bugs

1440
01:47:15,773 --> 01:47:17,441
It can't be helped

1441
01:47:18,309 --> 01:47:20,571
It's to protect thousands of people's lives

1442
01:47:20,778 --> 01:47:21,999
Isn't there any other way?

1443
01:47:42,751 --> 01:47:43,557
Today, again!

1444
01:47:43,896 --> 01:47:45,921
A numerous number of criminals are killed

1445
01:47:51,776 --> 01:47:52,436
Ryuzaki

1446
01:47:53,385 --> 01:47:55,544
You may be right to stop Kira from killing people

1447
01:47:56,928 --> 01:47:59,587
I'll take responsibility for the experiment

1448
01:47:59,784 --> 01:48:01,215
I'll supervise

1449
01:48:02,524 --> 01:48:03,080
Dad..

1450
01:48:04,230 --> 01:48:06,074
Thank you for understanding

1451
01:48:06,791 --> 01:48:08,612
I'll goto the States

1452
01:48:08,760 --> 01:48:10,127
Are you going alone?

1453
01:48:11,166 --> 01:48:12,531
Let me go with you

1454
01:48:12,764 --> 01:48:13,798
No, you can't

1455
01:48:14,766 --> 01:48:17,206
Stay here with Ryuzaki and wait until I contact you

1456
01:48:18,698 --> 01:48:19,910
I'll be fine

1457
01:48:20,478 --> 01:48:22,663
Others will come with me, little to worry

1458
01:48:23,229 --> 01:48:24,844
Wait, am I worrying?

1459
01:48:27,251 --> 01:48:27,937
How about here?

1460
01:48:28,360 --> 01:48:29,356
Yes, it is worrying

1461
01:48:34,786 --> 01:48:38,742
First, goto the Tokyo Bay heliport by car

1462
01:48:40,579 --> 01:48:45,903
Then fly to the Yokota Camp. The US army will carry you by plane to Washington D.C.

1463
01:48:47,460 --> 01:48:49,000
Watari has arranged for everything

1464
01:48:49,519 --> 01:48:50,123
I got it

1465
01:48:50,768 --> 01:48:52,096
See you later

1466
01:49:20,765 --> 01:49:22,600
Now, we're all alone

1467
01:49:23,768 --> 01:49:25,624
What are you thinking about?

1468
01:49:26,771 --> 01:49:27,987
Right now

1469
01:49:28,514 --> 01:49:30,606
Watari is coming here Amane

1470
01:49:32,035 --> 01:49:33,663
It was your plan!

1471
01:49:35,019 --> 01:49:35,889
Why Misa?

1472
01:49:36,781 --> 01:49:41,498
For some reason, the 13 day rule didn't work for Amane

1473
01:49:42,702 --> 01:49:44,872
Amane is the Second Kira

1474
01:49:45,642 --> 01:49:47,930
And she has another Death Note

1475
01:49:48,362 --> 01:49:50,151
This is what I'm thinking about

1476
01:49:51,092 --> 01:49:56,684
Then why she didn't write your name when she was freed?

1477
01:49:57,196 --> 01:50:01,289
Probably, she forgot my name she saw at the college

1478
01:50:01,858 --> 01:50:03,979
while she was restrained

1479
01:50:05,729 --> 01:50:07,924
Forgetting things is a girl's nature

1480
01:50:11,477 --> 01:50:12,911
I am going to

1481
01:50:12,946 --> 01:50:15,163
show my face to Amane

1482
01:50:17,627 --> 01:50:18,703
What?

1483
01:50:19,420 --> 01:50:20,817
If you do that, she'll...

1484
01:50:21,318 --> 01:50:23,163
Yes, she'll definitely write my name..

1485
01:50:23,198 --> 01:50:25,738
We can catch her when she's done it

1486
01:50:26,256 --> 01:50:29,687
Let's get her Note

1487
01:50:30,721 --> 01:50:32,763
We never know when and when she'll write

1488
01:50:33,167 --> 01:50:36,688
There are millions of cameras in this building

1489
01:50:36,727 --> 01:50:38,778
What if she didn't bring the Note?

1490
01:50:38,813 --> 01:50:40,588
She'll definitely bring it. This is a huge chance

1491
01:50:41,392 --> 01:50:42,762
to kill me

1492
01:50:46,737 --> 01:50:47,553
All right!

1493
01:50:48,381 --> 01:50:50,537
Then we'll catch her, and restrain her again

1494
01:50:50,572 --> 01:50:52,379
until she tells us about the First Kira

1495
01:50:52,882 --> 01:50:53,944
Is that alright?

1496
01:50:54,712 --> 01:50:56,818
We can definitely make her confess

1497
01:50:57,352 --> 01:50:58,352
as we have the evidence

1498
01:50:59,157 --> 01:51:01,966
You shut out the crew to do this, didn't you?

1499
01:51:02,720 --> 01:51:04,597
If she'll be tied like that again

1500
01:51:05,286 --> 01:51:07,391
She may die this time

1501
01:51:08,546 --> 01:51:10,514
I know I feel sorry, but it can't be helped

1502
01:51:20,968 --> 01:51:22,677
What's the matter Death God?

1503
01:51:35,413 --> 01:51:37,667
Ryuzaki asked me to come

1504
01:51:38,425 --> 01:51:41,651
does it mean he doesn't suspect me as Kira anymore?

1505
01:51:42,298 --> 01:51:43,376
Of course, he doesn't

1506
01:51:57,741 --> 01:51:58,690
But if...

1507
01:51:59,764 --> 01:52:02,078
I couldn't save your life...

1508
01:52:02,713 --> 01:52:05,145
If my heart stops

1509
01:52:05,716 --> 01:52:07,830
this sensor will automatically alert Mr. Yagami

1510
01:52:08,719 --> 01:52:11,266
I've asked him to burn the Death Note

1511
01:52:11,687 --> 01:52:13,979
to never be used again

1512
01:52:19,180 --> 01:52:21,771
Misa's lifespan has been shortened again

1513
01:52:23,982 --> 01:52:24,822
Lifespan?

1514
01:52:25,538 --> 01:52:26,166
What do you mean?

1515
01:52:26,622 --> 01:52:27,195
Ryuzaki

1516
01:52:28,739 --> 01:52:31,054
If you risk your life I'm prepared too

1517
01:52:32,218 --> 01:52:33,728
Let's catch Amane Misa

1518
01:52:33,763 --> 01:52:36,289
...the Second Kira in the act!

1519
01:52:42,427 --> 01:52:43,099
Here she comes

1520
01:53:05,743 --> 01:53:07,697
Yagami Light....

1521
01:53:08,425 --> 01:53:11,078
You've known that this would happen

1522
01:53:12,134 --> 01:53:16,444
Since when I told you that if a Death God expands lifespan of a human

1523
01:53:17,007 --> 01:53:17,838
the Death God will die

1524
01:53:21,195 --> 01:53:23,209
You drove her intoa a corner

1525
01:53:23,244 --> 01:53:24,860
to make me save her

1526
01:53:25,664 --> 01:53:27,815
It will expand her lifespan

1527
01:53:28,499 --> 01:53:29,499
and I will die instead

1528
01:53:31,013 --> 01:53:34,564
That's been your plan from that day

1529
01:53:35,720 --> 01:53:38,180
You'll succeed in killing a Death God!

1530
01:53:39,099 --> 01:53:41,668
You are the true devil

1531
01:53:43,552 --> 01:53:46,597
But still, Misa loves you

1532
01:53:48,523 --> 01:53:49,703
Yagami Light!

1533
01:53:50,517 --> 01:53:53,587
I'll never let you use my Note!

1534
01:53:55,008 --> 01:53:55,780
Misa...

1535
01:53:57,038 --> 01:53:58,398
Even if a short while...

1536
01:53:58,433 --> 01:53:59,766
be happy...

1537
01:54:16,257 --> 01:54:17,101
Watari...!

1538
01:54:17,707 --> 01:54:18,703
Checkmate..!

1539
01:54:43,690 --> 01:54:44,691
Did you use...

1540
01:54:44,726 --> 01:54:45,663
that Death God...?

1541
01:54:48,386 --> 01:54:50,802
Rem has a gentle heart

1542
01:54:52,996 --> 01:54:54,298
Yagami Light...

1543
01:54:57,721 --> 01:54:58,448
I knew it...

1544
01:54:58,645 --> 01:54:59,849
You are the Kira

1545
01:55:00,064 --> 01:55:01,796
I wanted to know your name

1546
01:55:04,315 --> 01:55:05,072
Loser

1547
01:55:07,315 --> 01:55:08,665
I am

1548
01:55:10,699 --> 01:55:11,917
not a...

1549
01:55:20,813 --> 01:55:22,781
Goodbye, L

1550
01:55:24,404 --> 01:55:27,303
You were the best rival

1551
01:55:27,789 --> 01:55:29,256
of me, Kira, the God of the new world.

1552
01:55:30,675 --> 01:55:32,106
If I made a single mistake

1553
01:55:32,959 --> 01:55:34,949
I might've been dead too

1554
01:55:36,625 --> 01:55:38,853
It was a high risk to release Misa

1555
01:55:40,095 --> 01:55:44,891
and let her use Death Note instead of me

1556
01:55:47,730 --> 01:55:50,796
Keep watching me achieving the revolution

1557
01:55:52,433 --> 01:55:55,232
Farewell, L.

1558
01:55:57,747 --> 01:55:58,468
I see...

1559
01:55:58,469 --> 01:56:03,662
She burnt the Note with her

1560
01:56:08,568 --> 01:56:09,526
Light!

1561
01:56:09,561 --> 01:56:10,405
You made it!

1562
01:56:10,440 --> 01:56:11,290
Misa, where's the Note?

1563
01:56:17,631 --> 01:56:19,800
So, you killed L!

1564
01:56:19,801 --> 01:56:21,675
Ryuk! How have you been?

1565
01:56:22,257 --> 01:56:23,860
I won, L is dead

1566
01:56:24,443 --> 01:56:25,688
But I still have a job

1567
01:56:31,490 --> 01:56:33,792
"Yagami Soichiro"

1568
01:56:37,344 --> 01:56:38,765
"Heart attack"

1569
01:56:40,180 --> 01:56:41,867
That's your own father's name, Light!

1570
01:56:42,585 --> 01:56:44,013
To create the new world

1571
01:56:45,590 --> 01:56:46,401
But

1572
01:56:49,716 --> 01:56:51,080
He's your father!

1573
01:56:51,926 --> 01:56:52,834
Why!

1574
01:56:52,835 --> 01:56:54,728
Just shut up!

1575
01:56:55,846 --> 01:56:57,301
No matter how you love something,

1576
01:56:58,269 --> 01:56:59,867
there's the time you have make sacrifices

1577
01:57:01,958 --> 01:57:03,602
I cannot be what I used to be

1578
01:57:09,092 --> 01:57:14,302
"Comes back with the Death Note, gives it to Light and dies"

1579
01:57:46,001 --> 01:57:46,716
Dad...

1580
01:57:56,489 --> 01:57:58,294
Give the Death Note back to me

1581
01:58:02,353 --> 01:58:03,082
Dad

1582
01:58:05,402 --> 01:58:07,453
Since we were young

1583
01:58:08,142 --> 01:58:09,708
You don't forgive even the most insignificant injustice

1584
01:58:10,820 --> 01:58:12,314
and try to be our model father

1585
01:58:13,723 --> 01:58:15,736
I respect you so much

1586
01:58:17,477 --> 01:58:19,299
So I'm sure you'll understand

1587
01:58:20,720 --> 01:58:22,247
What I'm going to do

1588
01:58:24,320 --> 01:58:25,384
What I will achieve

1589
01:58:29,682 --> 01:58:30,291
Dad...

1590
01:58:33,686 --> 01:58:36,705
I'm sorry

1591
01:58:37,630 --> 01:58:38,619
It's your time

1592
01:58:51,195 --> 01:58:52,329
Where's the Death Note?

1593
01:58:52,611 --> 01:58:53,140
Light

1594
01:58:55,286 --> 01:58:56,538
I saw everything

1595
01:59:01,057 --> 01:59:02,360
I watched you through the cameras

1596
01:59:04,237 --> 01:59:05,420
and I heard your voice

1597
01:59:06,418 --> 01:59:07,175
What?

1598
01:59:17,563 --> 01:59:18,546
Light!

1599
01:59:20,155 --> 01:59:21,223
Light!

1600
01:59:22,886 --> 01:59:23,778
You're...

1601
01:59:24,996 --> 01:59:25,844
under arrest

1602
01:59:29,675 --> 01:59:31,276
Light,

1603
01:59:33,264 --> 01:59:34,294
I'm so sad

1604
01:59:35,181 --> 01:59:35,923
we couldn't be friends

1605
01:59:39,685 --> 01:59:40,840
Ryuzaki...?

1606
01:59:43,726 --> 01:59:44,682
You...

1607
01:59:46,376 --> 01:59:47,124
Why...

1608
01:59:53,982 --> 01:59:55,344
A fake notebook!

1609
01:59:57,231 --> 01:59:58,258
Misa, you betrayed me!

1610
02:00:00,001 --> 02:00:00,981
No, I didn't

1611
02:00:02,696 --> 02:00:04,647
How can I betray you?

1612
02:00:05,678 --> 02:00:09,248
No matter how evil you are

1613
02:00:10,775 --> 02:00:12,076
I love you!

1614
02:00:15,322 --> 02:00:17,760
She didn't betray you

1615
02:00:19,500 --> 02:00:22,409
It was unexpected that the Death God acted that way

1616
02:00:25,514 --> 02:00:26,984
This is the real one

1617
02:00:27,516 --> 02:00:29,909
Amane Misa digged out

1618
02:00:32,507 --> 02:00:33,460
And this

1619
02:00:34,456 --> 02:00:37,470
is my real name, which you wanted to know

1620
02:00:41,530 --> 02:00:44,975
You can't change what is written in the Death Note

1621
02:00:45,534 --> 02:00:48,827
which means you won't die until the day written first

1622
02:00:49,538 --> 02:00:52,748
I'll die 20 days later

1623
02:00:53,938 --> 02:00:55,993
so you can't kill me now

1624
02:00:57,513 --> 02:00:58,732
when did you switch them?

1625
02:00:59,515 --> 02:01:02,232
The criminals I punished died as planned

1626
02:01:03,519 --> 02:01:05,010
Yes, on the first day

1627
02:01:05,977 --> 02:01:09,603
Then I concluded that you are the Second Kira

1628
02:01:10,526 --> 02:01:13,007
The 13 day rule is also false

1629
02:01:13,529 --> 02:01:16,360
From the second day, Watari switched it into the fake one

1630
02:01:17,082 --> 02:01:19,175
We were watching it

1631
02:01:20,036 --> 02:01:22,318
and told you a false information

1632
02:01:23,249 --> 02:01:26,807
as if the criminals were killed by Kira

1633
02:01:27,350 --> 02:01:29,507
The biggest goal was, Light

1634
02:01:29,783 --> 02:01:32,935
to confirm that you're Kira

1635
02:01:33,765 --> 02:01:35,298
You're a smart boy

1636
02:01:35,889 --> 02:01:37,438
You didn't give me any clue

1637
02:01:37,996 --> 02:01:39,020
So I decided

1638
02:01:41,009 --> 02:01:42,967
to give up my own life

1639
02:01:43,773 --> 02:01:47,227
This plan couldn't succeed without Mr. Yagami's cooperation

1640
02:01:48,462 --> 02:01:51,160
He is a very sincere person. At first he refused to do it

1641
02:01:51,972 --> 02:01:54,298
But when I showed him my name written in the Note

